# Rarities
[Git Source](https://github.com/ECHOCODE33/RetroPunks-Lab/blob/53dba76e70625b47f9afcf8f21d96497afb9c7a7/src/Rarities.sol)

**Title:**
Rarities

**Author:**
ECHO

Rarities for the RetroPunks collection, optimized for gas efficiency

Rarity values are stored in bytes arrays and selected using a PRNG for gas efficiency
